Fully hand written 3D rendering-engine in C
rasterization using the "scanline" technique
linear algebra library
space transformation (world/view)
2d screen projection
fully functional 3D camera
Adjustable FOV
Programatic resolution-scaling
Depth checking with painter's algorithm
Wireframe rendering
Backface culling
User input through keyboard/mouse
Support for loading in OBJ-files
Triangle clipping
Basic diffuse lighting (flat shaded)